<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Asesoría Hardware | TechRM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0c10;
            --bg-panel: #11131a;
            --card-bg: #171923;
            --card-inner: #202431;
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --accent-blue: #7fc7ff;
            --accent-green: #7dd3a8;
            --accent-amber: #f4c56a;
            --nav-bg: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            background: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .advice-hero {
            min-height: 620px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(360px, 0.95fr);
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            padding: 9rem 6% 5rem;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 18% 28%, rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.22), transparent 32%),
                linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(16, 13, 8, 1), rgba(26, 20, 10, 0.98) 52%, rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.94));
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .hero-copy { max-width: 720px; }

        .eyebrow {
            color: var(--accent-amber);
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        }

        .advice-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.3rem);
            line-height: 0.98;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .advice-hero h1 span { color: var(--accent-amber); }

        .hero-copy p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 620px;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-service {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.35rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-service:hover,
        .btn-service:focus {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.55);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        }

        .btn-primary-service {
            background: var(--accent-amber);
            color: #3a2500;
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        .lead-form {
            align-self: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.34);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(26, 20, 10, 0.9);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        }

        .lead-form h2 {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
        }

        .lead-form p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #ffe7ba;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        input,
        select,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 0.82rem 0.9rem;
        }

        textarea { resize: vertical; }

        .form-submit {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 46px;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--accent-amber);
            color: #3a2500;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .success-banner {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 0.9rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.42);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.12);
            color: #bdf4d0;
            font-size: 0.86rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .decision-panel {
            align-self: stretch;
            min-height: 420px;
            display: grid;
            align-content: end;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(23, 25, 35, 0.12), rgba(23, 25, 35, 0.9)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
            position: relative;
        }

        .decision-panel::before {
            content: "CPU  GPU  RAM  PSU  SSD";
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            left: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.28);
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.78);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1.4px;
            word-spacing: 1.2rem;
            background: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.36);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .panel-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.78);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .panel-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .panel-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1180px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-heading {
            display: flex;
            align-items: end;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-heading h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        .section-heading p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 460px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .advice-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .advice-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.35rem;
        }

        .advice-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent-amber);
            color: #3a2500;
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .advice-tag.blue { background: var(--accent-blue); color: #08233d; }
        .advice-tag.green { background: var(--accent-green); color: #082411; }

        .advice-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        }

        .advice-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
        }

        .compare-section {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .compare-image {
            min-height: 430px;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.08), rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.68)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555617981-dac3880eac6e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
        }

        .compare-list {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .compare-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            background: var(--bg-panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.25rem;
        }

        .compare-item strong {
            width: 34px;
            height: 34px;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent-amber);
            color: #3a2500;
        }

        .compare-item h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
        }

        .compare-item p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.86rem;
        }

        .cta-panel {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(244, 197, 106, 0.14), var(--bg-panel));
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .cta-panel h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .cta-panel p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 3rem 6%;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .light-mode {
            --bg-color: #f7f9fc;
            --bg-panel: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: #f8f9fa;
            --card-inner: #ffffff;
            --card-border: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.12);
            --text-main: #172033;
            --text-muted: #4b5565;
            --accent-blue: #0b74d1;
            --accent-green: #15803d;
            --accent-amber: #b45309;
            --nav-bg: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .light-mode .advice-hero {
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 18% 28%, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.14), transparent 32%),
                linear-gradient(145deg, #fffaf2, #fff7e8 52%, #f7f9fc);
        }

        .light-mode .decision-panel::before {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);
            color: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.82);
        }

        .light-mode .decision-panel {
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
        }

        .light-mode .panel-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        }

        .light-mode .lead-form {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            border-color: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.22);
        }

        .light-mode .form-group label {
            color: #67410f;
        }

        .light-mode input,
        .light-mode select,
        .light-mode textarea {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-color: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.14);
        }

        .light-mode .success-banner {
            background: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.24);
            color: #166534;
        }

        .light-mode .compare-image {
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.32)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555617981-dac3880eac6e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
            filter: saturate(1.06) contrast(1.02) brightness(1.03);
        }

        .light-mode .cta-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.1), #ffffff);
        }

        .light-mode .nav-links a.active {
            color: #0b74d1;
            border-bottom-color: #0b74d1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .advice-hero,
            .compare-section,
            .cta-panel {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .decision-panel { min-height: 320px; }
            .advice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .lead-form { align-self: auto; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .advice-hero {
                padding: 8rem 1.25rem 3rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .advice-grid,
            .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .section-heading { display: block; }
            .section-heading p { margin-top: 1rem; }
            .container { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
            footer { flex-direction: column; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <header class="advice-hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
            <div class="eyebrow">Asesoría hardware</div>
            <h1>Compra componentes con menos dudas y más <span>criterio.</span></h1>
            <p>Te ayudamos a decidir si merece la pena actualizar, reparar, montar desde cero o esperar. La idea es gastar donde se nota y evitar piezas incompatibles.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="#solicitud">Pedir asesoría</a>
                <a class="btn-service" href="/hardware">Volver a hardware</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <form class="lead-form" id="solicitud" action="/solicitar-asesoria-hardware" method="POST">
            <h2>Resuelve tu duda antes de comprar</h2>
            <p>Cuéntanos qué tienes en mente y te ayudamos a elegir el camino correcto.</p>
            <% if (typeof success !== 'undefined' && success) { %>
                <div class="success-banner">Solicitud enviada. Te responderemos lo antes posible.</div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Tu nombre" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="contacto">Contacto</label>
                    <input type="text" id="contacto" name="contacto" placeholder="Email o teléfono" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="objetivo">Objetivo</label>
                    <select id="objetivo" name="objetivo">
                        <option>Comprar piezas</option>
                        <option>Actualizar mi equipo</option>
                        <option>Comparar presupuestos</option>
                        <option>No estoy seguro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="presupuesto">Presupuesto</label>
                    <input type="text" id="presupuesto" name="presupuesto" placeholder="Ej: 800€">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="detalles">Duda principal</label>
                <textarea id="detalles" name="detalles" rows="3" placeholder="Piezas que estás mirando, equipo actual o uso que le darás..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <button class="form-submit" type="submit">Pedir asesoría</button>
        </form>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="decisiones">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Qué resolvemos</h2>
                <p>La asesoría convierte una lista de dudas en una decisión clara, con prioridades y opciones realistas.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="advice-grid">
                <article class="advice-card">
                    <span class="advice-tag">Comprar</span>
                    <h3>Elegir componentes compatibles</h3>
                    <p>Revisamos CPU, GPU, placa, RAM, caja, fuente, refrigeración y almacenamiento antes de comprar.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="advice-card">
                    <span class="advice-tag blue">Actualizar</span>
                    <h3>Mejorar sin cambiarlo todo</h3>
                    <p>Detectamos qué pieza limita el equipo y qué mejora tendrá impacto real en rendimiento.</p>
                </article>

                <article class="advice-card">
                    <span class="advice-tag green">Ahorrar</span>
                    <h3>Evitar gasto innecesario</h3>
                    <p>Comparamos alternativas y separamos lo imprescindible de lo que solo encarece la compra.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="compare-section">
            <div class="compare-image" aria-label="Comparativa de componentes de hardware"></div>
            <div class="compare-list">
                <article class="compare-item">
                    <strong>1</strong>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Presupuesto con sentido</h3>
                        <p>Distribuimos el dinero según el uso: no todas las tareas necesitan la misma GPU, RAM o CPU.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="compare-item">
                    <strong>2</strong>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Compatibilidad revisada</h3>
                        <p>Comprobamos socket, tamaño de caja, consumo, BIOS, conectores y refrigeración.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="compare-item">
                    <strong>3</strong>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Plan de evolución</h3>
                        <p>Si no conviene comprar todo ahora, dejamos una ruta por fases para ampliar más adelante.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-panel">
            <div>
                <h2>¿Ya tienes una lista de piezas?</h2>
                <p>Puedes usar la asesoría como paso previo al montaje. Revisamos la configuración y, si encaja, pasas al montaje con una base sólida.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="/montaje">Ver montaje</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="logo">TECHRM</div>
        <div>© 2026 TECHRM. Asesoría clara antes de comprar hardware.</div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
